rComments: Professor Matthews is probably one of the most respected faculties. He is always friendly and enthusiastic. You can actually feel that he wants you to succeed as long as you participate in class and communicate with him after class.

Is he still teaching?  I had him for several classes about 4 years ago and I think of him often.  He was one of my most inspiring profs ever.  I'd love to speak with him again.  If you have the chance, take a course with him.  After so many years in such a frustrating field, he is optimistic and realistic, not to mention a clear and fair professor.
Great prof, great guy. Still a pinnacle in African studies.
An experienced prof with a deep knowledge and passion for Africa. The only problem was that he let people with nothing interesting to say say it anyways.

You can tell how much he cares about Africa, and he inspires an enthusiasm for the topic in just about all his students.  He is by far the kindest, most interesting, most helpful prof I have ever had.
I LOVED HIM!! He is the best!!!! If you love Africa go and talk to Bob Matthews!!! A brilliant prof!
Clear, focussed and secinct. An excellent lecturer and a thorough grader.
